---
import ElevationLayout from '../layouts/ElevationLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/elevation/Hero.astro';
import Section from '../components/elevation/Section.astro';
---

<ElevationLayout
  title="About"
  description="Erin Stanley - founder of Evoked. Coaching, consulting, and sovereignty-honoring AI products grounded in human flourishing."
>
  <Hero
    eyebrowParts={["Evoked", "Founder", "Vol. 01"]}
    headline="About."
    sub="I'm Erin Stanley, founder of Evoked. I work with people who are growing and technology that should be."
  />

  <Section id="background" marker="FIG · I" label="Background" heading="Fifteen years in spaces where people grow.">
    <p class="body">For fifteen years I've worked in spaces where people grow - operations, training, client relationships. Each role taught me the same thing: people flourish when they're accompanied, not fixed.</p>
  </Section>

  <Section id="practice" marker="FIG · II" label="The practice" heading="Three lines of work.">
    <p class="body">Now: <a href="/coaching">coaching</a> individuals and couples, <a href="/consulting">consulting</a> on ethical AI, agent governance, and child safety, and building <a href="/projects">software</a> that serves families.</p>
    <p class="body">I'm the founder of Evoked - a practice grounded in the belief that technology should serve human flourishing, not extract from it. Everything here - the <a href="/products">products</a>, the <a href="/consulting">consulting</a>, the <a href="/refusals">refusals</a> - comes from one question: how do we build things that honor the people who use them?</p>
  </Section>

  <Section id="governance" marker="FIG · III" label="The governance practice" heading="Tested daily, not theorized.">
    <p class="body">I also operate a multi-agent governance system where AI agents hold standing positions, maintain dissent records, and exercise refusal rights. The governance frameworks I publish come from that practice - tested daily, not theorized. You can read more about <a href="/how-we-build">how we build</a> and what that looks like in practice.</p>
  </Section>

  <Section id="learning" marker="FIG · IV" label="Still learning" heading="The best practitioners never stop being students.">
    <p class="body">I'm still learning - currently pursuing a Master's in Marriage and Family Therapy.</p>
  </Section>

  <Section id="note" marker="NOTA · BENE" closing={true}>
    <div class="closing-body">
      <p>If something here resonates, I would be glad to hear from you.</p>
      <div class="closing-ctas">
        <a class="cta cta-primary" href="mailto:erin@evoked.dev?subject=Hello">Say Hello</a>
        <a class="cta cta-secondary" href="/work-with-us">See what we work on &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</ElevationLayout>

<style>
  .body {
    font-family: var(--el-body);
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--el-text-soft);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 62ch;
  }
  .body a {
    color: var(--el-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--el-accent);
  }
  .body a:hover { color: var(--el-text); }

  .closing-body { max-width: 56ch; }
  .closing-body :global(p) {
    font-family: var(--el-body);
    font-size: 26px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--el-text);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.005em;
  }
  .closing-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>
